{"tid":2098427,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解「基本完成」「基本優質」係大陸中文？","createTime":"2020-07-07T13:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T10:02:16.000Z","uid":39021,"like":147,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"fb552f89fdaa86db1e10f68e8741182b580f0248","tid":2098427,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"大陸中文，並非只係用字問題，最大特點其實係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過度簡化</span></strong>（就好似簡體字咁）<br />\n文革後大量文人被批鬥走，剩返一堆讀書少既紅衛兵，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">偏向用簡單詞語取替各有nuance既詞語</span></strong><br />\n「打造」係公認既大陸中文，但其實「打造」本身係無辜，古代已經有用<br />\n<code>《三國演義&middot;第一回》：「玄德謝別二客，便命良匠打造雙股劍。」</code><br />\n真正問題係在於，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大陸中文用「打造」兩個字取替晒所有「Ｘ造」</span></strong>（創造，建造，塑造，修造，鑄造，締造），<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簡化咗語句本身既意思</span></strong><br />\n不斷簡化，最終只會引致言辭不清，語義模糊<br />\n<br />\n咁點解「基本完成」「基本優質」係大陸中文？其實亦都同過份簡化用字有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先黎睇睇例子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2097497/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2097497/page/1</a><br />\n呢個post樓主講咗句<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">利申，創業撚，公司依家十幾人，業務結構基本成形</code></pre><br />\n有位巴打咁樣屌佢<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">基本成形係咩品種既狗話黎?</code></pre><br />\n結果呢位巴位唔知點解遭受大量負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地又可以睇睇Google Ngram分析簡體中文（Ngram冇繁體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）近年既演變<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6ZUxzs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6ZUxzs.png&h=18b9e42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺簡體詞彙入面，「基本上」呢個用法已經被「基本乜乜」取代咗<br />\n<br />\n巴打就會話，「我係鍾意唔講個上字呀，關你撚事咩，矯枉過正！」<br />\n如果巴打試下跳出一步睇「基本」兩個字，就會知道個「上」字點解咁重要<br />\n「基本」可作名詞，如：<em>國家之基本</em><br />\n「基本」可作形容詞，有時會附上「的」，如：<em>基本的知識</em>／<em>基本知識</em>，<em>呢啲數學好基本姐</em><br />\n作副詞時，取basically之義，一般要寫成「基本上」，如：<em>基本上搞掂晒</em>，<em>基本上場波已經輸咗</em>／<em>場波基本上已經輸咗</em><br />\n加「上」字，其實係要將副詞用法同名詞形容詞用法區別開去<br />\n如果「基本」可以直接當埋副詞咁去用（如：基本搞掂晒、場波基本輸咗），咁<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「基本」就可以同時以三種形態出現，長久落去，文章就容易會睇到混淆，因為讀者要好仔細睇，先知道究竟「基本」係以咩形式呈現意義</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就算係日文都會分清楚三種用法，分類方法仲要同香港中文好似（由上到下：形容／名詞，形容詞，副詞）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCw0tgB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCw0tgB.png&h=f7c51933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸中文從好多方面影響香港中文，並非只係避開大陸詞彙就足夠<br />\n我地要理解點解大陸中文破壞力咁大，先可以避免自己言辭不清，語義模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0287cd25370ae7248a6a657c84048bb481c388c1","tid":2098427,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90186a54da9b2199f6214e8d5fb3ae7e1053e069","tid":2098427,"uid":39021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"事實上「基本」／「基本上」涉及好多問題，大家本身有唔同意見都好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3b851c28fe69df1fdff14078912e94a22b08e5","tid":2098427,"uid":6741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n支持學好中文<br />\n<br />\n唔可以任由支共敗壞我哋嘅語言"},{"pid":"3662ca4956283523df1e5395d62ae080c52fd033","tid":2098427,"uid":70342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:06:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73fc40d79a35980793017281cd4d3b5771aaf3ca","tid":2098427,"uid":66049,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"我都睇過嗰個post<br />\n乜撚嘢基本完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967f46b6f30f35b905dae3bc4b416a4b40381576","tid":2098427,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"承傳優良中文，係要透過一連串討論先可以明事理，大家記得唔好互相批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d66e10112e569a1e6cb0b48ac912a5e650a12f","tid":2098427,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66abb885a515631f6cacd2c5871626fc97d83108","tid":2098427,"uid":244832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b252292531db4885582ded68e7f2479afb38311","tid":2098427,"uid":39021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"66abb885a515631f6cacd2c5871626fc97d83108","tid":2098427,"uid":244832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:13:07.000Z","msg":"見到post入面位巴打咁樣比人負評，心有不甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />決定拔刀相助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21040652887a3f04b5ec1ee30018e3c63516b97","tid":2098427,"uid":31575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"巴打好波<br />\n睇到d盲毛鳩屌就燥"},{"pid":"d98d50655ab0a1d236f9c1914a6fa59a88ac8a02","tid":2098427,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:22:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望巴打出多啲咁嘅post"},{"pid":"f04403b44bf1288a82e6eecea097126a8ac30248","tid":2098427,"uid":229492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2653dff1fb2e66262cbf2c7dcbfd8951363f3e07","tid":2098427,"uid":39021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d98d50655ab0a1d236f9c1914a6fa59a88ac8a02","tid":2098427,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:22:06.000Z","msg